{"tid":2024274,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"曼德拉基金會: 翻查資料庫 均沒有發現該句說話","createTime":"2020-05-19T13:33:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-20T01:40:49.000Z","uid":5195,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"6b88f36de6d6dd9f0b29cf7aaf8245509ad0c196","tid":2024274,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T13:33:45.000Z","msg":"特首辦今晚（19日）回覆明報網站查詢，稱就特首今早的引述，特首辦留意到從網上搜尋，該引述是有不同版本和出處，樂意接受指正，並對若因此引起的誤會表示歉意。特首辦又表示，曼德拉有教無類的教育理念舉世公認，而教育對任何國家及地方的重要性也是毋庸置疑，特區政府同樣十分重視教育，教育當局將繼續肩負確保教育質素的責任。<br />\n<br />\n本報向曼德拉基金會求證該引述是否出自曼德拉，曼德拉基金會檔案館館長Razia Saleh回覆稱，曾翻查逾1500多篇曼德拉演辭的資料庫、曼德拉的名言書籍及作品，均沒有發現該句說話。Razia Saleh又表示，多年來遇過不少無法證明的曼德拉名言，該句話說是其中之一。<br />\n<br />\n明報"},{"pid":"10702b43b0c1951a51d7f6ca23fdf121baf3c959","tid":2024274,"uid":281020,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T13:37:35.000Z","msg":"個基金會中咗孟加拉效應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c80608c6fff954836424f42513b9779db1a4c884","tid":2024274,"uid":88743,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T13:43:03.000Z","msg":"曼德拉效應<br />\n<br />\n証明後人同當權者操控真相<br />\n絕對係可行"},{"pid":"d1233e6e139f16c6d2cddc3cf0facef0cad1a3e5","tid":2024274,"uid":37389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T13:45:26.000Z","msg":"曼德拉效應原來係咁解。。。"},{"pid":"82374087cc757d3b73aa11bd741b5e2876c8178e","tid":2024274,"uid":228868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T13:50:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d7faf7fdf175cd06e39456b0afb3ac98d3c5dea","tid":2024274,"uid":28432,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T13:55:36.000Z","msg":"林鄭又發放假消息<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"